title: Logo for online printing service
content:
Hi Typophiles

I've been working on this logo for a online printing service. I'm pretty stuck.

Info on the logo, is in the image on the right.

What do you think? Please help...

 ![](http://web.archive.org/web/20131031224617im_/http:/typophile.com/files/typophile_5427.jpg)

Thanks in advance - ZUZ3L
author: ZUZ3L

comments.content:
Since you're not getting any feedback I suppose people think "Go back to pencil and paper"

Your flower's maybe a bit too stylised to be recognised as a flower.  
\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_\_  
_Robert Koritnik_

and the type is distracting. going back to the sketch pad is a good suggestion.
